text: Justin Krewson (born July 24, 1996) is an American luger. He competed in the men's doubles event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:American male lugers Category:Olympic lugers of the United States Category:Lugers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
